    description: 'Your website isn\'t just a digital brochure‚Äîit\'s an intelligent system that learns, adapts, and works around the clock to grow your business.',
    icon: 'ü§ñ'
  },
  {
    title: 'Performance Obsessed',
    description: 'Every millisecond matters. We optimize images, code, and delivery to ensure your site is among the fastest on the web.',
